    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine runs consistently and the transmission shifts as expected, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dings, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind performing some cosmetic touch-ups and routine maintenance in the near future.",
      "price": 18500.0,
